                "invention-title": [
                    "Natural gas power generation combination system combining solar energy and wind energy",
                    "一种结合太阳能与风能的天然气发电联合系统"
                ]
            },
            "abstract": [
                {
                    "p": "The invention relates to the technical field of power generation, in particular to a natural gas power generation combination system combining solar energy and wind energy. The methane reforming reaction subsystem receives the radiation energy generated by the solar subsystem and converts the radiation energy into heat energy, and methane and water vapor are subjected to a chemical reaction to generate first hydrogen and carbon dioxide; the wind power hydrogen production subsystem generates electric energy by utilizing wind energy, and electrolyzes water by utilizing the electric energy to generate second hydrogen; the gas turbine subsystem is connected with the methane reforming reaction subsystem and the wind power hydrogen production subsystem; the gas turbine subsystem receives the first hydrogen, the second hydrogen, the first part of natural gas and the like as fuel for power generation; sufficient heat energy is provided for steam methane reforming through solar energy, electric energy is provided for hydrogen production through wind energy, fuel needed by a gas turbine subsystem is obtained, the use amount of natural gas is reduced, cost is reduced, and greenhouse gas emission is reduced."
                },
                {
                    "p": "本发明涉及发电技术领域，具体涉及一种结合太阳能与风能的天然气发电联合系统，包括：太阳能子系统；甲烷重整反应子系统接收太阳能子系统产生的辐射能，并转化为热能，将甲烷和水蒸气进行化学反应，生成第一氢气和二氧化碳；风力制氢子系统利用风能产生电能，再利用电能对水进行电解，生成第二氢气；燃气轮机子系统与甲烷重整反应子系统、风力制氢子系统均连接；燃气轮机子系统接收第一氢气、第二氢气和第一部分天然气等，作为燃料，用于发电；本申请利用太阳能为蒸汽甲烷重整提供充足的热能和利用风能为制氢提供电能，获得燃气轮机子系统所需要的燃料，降低天然气的使用量，降低成本，减少温室气体排放。"
                }
            ]
